StringLiteralExpr.value: Can only display a vector or two-dimensional matrix.
COL_STRINGS must be a cell array of strings, or a string with "|" as a delimiter.
ROW_STRINGS must be a cell array of strings, or a string with "|" as a delimiter.
COL_STRINGS must have one string per column of M, or be empty.
ROW_STRINGS must have one string per column of M, or be empty.
Format must be a format string or the number of significant digits (as in NUM2STR).
